{{wikipedia}}
'''ambergris'''
# {{uncountable}} A [[solid]], [[fatty]], [[flammable]] substance of a dull [[grey]] or [[black]]ish color, produced in the [[intestine]]s of the [[sperm whale]]. It is used in [[perfume]]s.

